dct_description_sm: Map of Ephriam's Island lying on the easterly side of Grassy Sound Channel opposite Holly Beach. The area that was removed by dredging is labeled. Flat Creek, Five Mile Beach Thoroughfare, and Holly Beach are identified. The edge of the broken bank and edge of grass are drawn
